				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The necro pet despawn was a hack put in ages ago. A high level necro could camp near a light blue spawn and go to sleep. The spawn would agro the pet, die, and the pet would be fully healed before the next spawn. It's completely outmoded now. Not only do pets not agro mobs but any remotely modern XP mob will eat the necro pet for lunch. So it's not an upgrade for necro's, it's just removing a hack that has no meaning any longer.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
